{"tid":1997557,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"4暴徒向警車擲汽油彈　1人被捕","createTime":"2020-05-01T17:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T18:45:23.000Z","uid":66507,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5877db21f7988ba79f52e66a795d162bb26bef","tid":1997557,"uid":66507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"昨晚(5月1日)11時許，一輛警車於旺角彌敦道與界限街交界，疑遭黑衣人投擲汽油彈，現場頓時火光熊熊，地上遺下玻璃樽碎片，事件中無人受傷。未幾，一輛載有數名便衣警員客貨車駛至增援，4名人士見狀逃走；便衣警員隨即追捕，終將其中一名人士截獲拘捕，帶署查問，其餘3名涉案同黨趁亂逃走，警方正追捕在逃人士歸案。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，事發時疑有黑衣人向警車投擲汽油彈，亦有人將插有鐵釘的膠管掟向警員，事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200502/mobile/bkn-20200502003810910-0502_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200502%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200502003810910-0502_00822_001.html&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw16NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=d274e7e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200502/mobile/bkn-20200502003810910-0502_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"12028f9e578f6afe2e22094e4d5c0ac94b936814","tid":1997557,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0baea8c860131488547d300ec9f47a38cf74e5c","tid":1997557,"uid":264783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:01:26.000Z","msg":"願手足平安"},{"pid":"4de193733ef1e38679427ba5abcf266150925961","tid":1997557,"uid":66507,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"(轉自天馬)<br />\n利申: 如5月1日有任何恐怖主義或暴力襲擊行動，必為黑警自編自導自演，與本和平活動無關。"},{"pid":"41ec43e04dae4123e9dbfe07e2404d3f01a96ed1","tid":1997557,"uid":4001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:05:34.000Z","msg":"文滙:好在都叫有啲野寫下"},{"pid":"972083ed10dd8ab7e4af11d91949af94eeca0163","tid":1997557,"uid":66507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:12:42.000